OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe Range pulls bikini and 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbride weight loss items    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Range has discontinued weight-loss 
OL,6, countdown coin savers in the shape of a
OL,7, bikini and a wedding dress, after      
OL,8, complaints over sexist body shaming.   
OL,10,FThe wall plaques include slots to stash
OL,11,F#1 for every pound of weight lost - up 
OL,12,Fto 40lb (18kg) on the bridal version.  
OL,14,FEmma Conway saw the items and asked if 
OL,15,Fthere were any for men. There were not.
OL,17,FShe said: "I left the shop shaking. In 
OL,18,F2022 a large chain is feeding into the 
OL,19,Fnarrative that women need to be        
OL,20,Fsmaller, to drop a dress size."        
